      <title>Office Candy: Knomo Notebook Sleeve</title>
      <link>http://www.alisonrothwell.com/discovering/office-candy-knomo-notebook-sleeve/</link>
      <comments>http://www.alisonrothwell.com/discovering/office-candy-knomo-notebook-sleeve/#comments</comments>
      <pubDate>Thu, 14 Oct 2010 09:50:05 +0000</pubDate>
      <dc:creator>SEO Alison</dc:creator>
      <category><![CDATA[Discovering]]></category>
      <category><![CDATA[Latest News]]></category>
      <category><![CDATA[handbags]]></category>
      <category><![CDATA[notebook sleeves]]></category>
      <category><![CDATA[office accessories]]></category>
      <category><![CDATA[office candy]]></category>
      <guid isPermaLink="false">http://www.alisonrothwell.com/?p=1124</guid>
      <description><![CDATA[I&#8217;m a sucker for a handbag, and as regular readers know, I&#8217;m always on the hunt for the perfect but durable work bag to store my ever increasing array of must-have tech gadgets. Last month I spoke at the Mumpreneur 10 Conference about my Seven Steps to Online Business Success System. The Conference also hosted [...]]]></description>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p></p>
<div id="attachment_1125" class="wp-caption alignleft" style="width: 200px">
	<a href="http://www.alisonrothwell.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/10/mumpreneur10award.jpg"><img class="size-full wp-image-1125" title="mumpreneur10award" src="http://www.alisonrothwell.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/10/mumpreneur10award.jpg" alt="mumpreneur10award Office Candy: Knomo Notebook Sleeve" width="200" height="200" /></a>
	<p class="wp-caption-text">Spot the Arm Candy</p>
</div>
<p>I&#8217;m a sucker for a handbag, and as regular readers know, I&#8217;m always on the hunt for the perfect but durable work bag to store my ever increasing array of must-have tech gadgets.</p>
<p>Last month I spoke at the Mumpreneur 10 Conference about my Seven Steps to Online Business Success System. The Conference also hosted the Mumpreneur Awards and I was thrilled to accept the Gold Award for Most Unique Product on behalf of Jac Waggett at <a title="changing bags" href="http://www.pacapod.com/shop/" target="_blank">baby changing bag</a>s business Pacapod. Jac sadly couldn&#8217;t make her moment of glory in person as she was actually showing Pacapod in Europe at Kind und Jugend to an admiring audience.</p>
<p>It was my absolute pleasure to pick up the award &#8211; and to my delight, kind hearted Jac offered me the pick of her prizes. Not having a bag to house my Macbook (as it was bought originally for my husband, who doesn&#8217;t &#8220;do&#8221; that kinda thang), I was more than happy to take collection of the fabulous <a title="laptop sleeve knomo" href="http://www.knomobags.com/uk/women/laptop-sleeves/13-inch/" target="_blank">laptop sleeve from Knomo</a> you can see clutched to my side in the photo opposite.</p>
<p>What can I say ? I&#8217;m a complete handbag freak &#8211; and this is one classy accessory.</p>
<p>The laptop sleeve has a purple nylon quilted exterior with leather trim, giving great protection for your notebook against bangs and knocks. The interior is a contrasting silver silky fabric, there&#8217;s an outside flap to stash cabiles and the like, complete with the same silver lining. A strong, detachable shoulder strap and retractable leather handle completes the design.</p>
<div id="attachment_1126" class="wp-caption alignleft" style="width: 300px">
	<a href="http://www.alisonrothwell.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/10/knomo-serra.jpg"><img class="size-medium wp-image-1126" title="knomo-serra" src="http://www.alisonrothwell.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/10/knomo-serra-300x300.jpg" alt="knomo serra 300x300 Office Candy: Knomo Notebook Sleeve" width="300" height="300" /></a>
	<p class="wp-caption-text">Have wheels, must travel</p>
</div>
<p>I wish I hadn&#8217;t stepped online though to check out the rest of the collection.</p>
<p>I&#8217;ve now spotted the <a title="Knomo Serra" href="http://www.knomobags.com/uk/women/bags/wheeled/serra-15.html/" target="_blank">perfect wheeled laptop and overnight case combi</a> which would be perfect for my upcoming US conference.</p>
<p>It has the same nylon quilting as the sleeves, and leather handles and trim &#8211; but a black exterior opens to reveal a flashy hot pink interior.</p>
<p>And it only weighs 6 lbs!</p>
<p>It&#8217;s £195 and available in black, brown and tomato red.</p>
<p>Just wondering if I can get a discount at the Airport. Sigh.</p>
<p>Knomo Laptop Sleeves &#8211; from £50.00.</p>

]]></content:encoded>
