<p><a title="Pen, Diary and Glasses" href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/46959536@N04/4827013488/" target="_blank"><img class="alignleft" src="http://farm5.static.flickr.com/4099/4827013488_60953318d3_m.jpg" border="0" alt="4827013488 60953318d3 m Special Offer: Start a Family Friendly Business"  title="Special Offer: Start a Family Friendly Business" /></a><br />
