<p><strong><em>If you want find a family friendly way to work, an empowering and hands-on book by flexible working experts Antonia Chitty and Helen Lindop can help. Antonia and Helen are on a mission to get 1000+ mums<br />
launching their own business, and have put together some bonus material to help.</em></strong></p>
