</ul>
<p><em>Buy the book <strong>today</strong> and you’ll also get</em></p>
<ul>
<li><em>An exclusive podcast of Antonia Chitty and Helen Lindop’s tips and      experience to help you create a successful business</em></li>
<li><em> The Mumpreneur Success      report: A factsheet of tips to back up the podcast</em></li>
