      <guid isPermaLink="false">http://www.alisonrothwell.com/?p=1077</guid>
      <description><![CDATA[One of the marketing blogs I love to read is IttyBiz from uber-marketeer Naomi Dunford. This week Naomi challenged her readers to answer a very scary question. &#8220;What do you actually do?&#8221; Since I am not a scaredy-cat, I thought I’d try and give it a shot. Here goes. What’s your game? What do you [...]]]></description>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p></p>
<p><a href="http://www.alisonrothwell.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/10/ittybizlogo.gif"><img class="alignleft size-medium wp-image-1078" title="ittybizlogo" src="http://www.alisonrothwell.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/10/ittybizlogo-300x153.gif" alt="ittybizlogo 300x153 The Post Where I answer the IttyBiz Meme" width="300" height="153" /></a>One of the marketing blogs I love to read is IttyBiz from uber-marketeer Naomi Dunford.</p>
<p>This week Naomi <a href="http://ittybiz.com/what-do-you-do/" target="_blank">challenged her readers to answer a  very scary question.</a><br />
&#8220;What do you actually do?&#8221;</p>
<p>Since I am not a  scaredy-cat, I thought I’d try and give it a shot. Here goes.</p>
<p><em>What’s your game? What do you do?</em></p>
<p>I help small businesses and solopreneurs who struggle to market their business online effectively and need to make more sales online quickly and consistently</p>
<p><em>Why do you do it? Do you love it, or do you just have one of those creepy knacks?</em></p>
<p>I love it &#8211; and I have a creepy knack!</p>
<p><em>Who are your customers? What kind of people would need or want what you offer?</em></p>
<p>They&#8217;re peeps who are just so busy doing their online sales thang that they need simple steps to follow that are proven to work that they can do themselves. Or, they can be part of the small gang who hire me exclusively to do it all for them .</p>
<p><em>What’s your marketing USP? Why should I buy from you instead of the other losers?</em></p>
<p>Well, I&#8217;ve walked the walk. I&#8217;ve set up two online bizz &#8211; and I learnt internet marketing from scratch myself. There&#8217;s not many peeps out there who understand how hard it is to run your own bizz and sell products online&#8230;<em> I genuinely enjoy helping people to crack internet marketing and get the online success they deserve<br />
</em></p>
<p><em>What’s next for you? What’s the big plan?</em></p>
<p>Hee hee. I have plans. lots of them. Stay tuned&#8230;</p>
<p>So, there you have it Naomi! Makes change from those super soppy &#8220;what&#8217;s your favorite kitten&#8221; type of memes <img src='http://www.alisonrothwell.com/wp-includes/images/smilies/icon_wink.gif' alt="icon wink The Post Where I answer the IttyBiz Meme" class='wp-smiley' title="The Post Where I answer the IttyBiz Meme" /> </p>

]]></content:encoded>
